#                    't_shyfem_ps2gif.man' task manual
#=========================================================================

This "ecFlow" task is aimed at running a job script, which creates a
customized GIF, from a PostScript obtained through the "shyplot" SHYFEM's
tool, applied to a SHY (.shy) file for a given time interval, variable
and vertical layer, and according to a parameter STR file for post
processing routines.
